<div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 py-10 min-h-screen bg-[#fcfaf7] pb-24">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-serif">
    今日も一日お疲れさま🌱
  </h1>

  <div class="flex items-baseline mb-6">
    <span class="text-3xl font-semibold mr-1">
      <%= current_user.name %>
    </span>
    <span class="text-stone-600">さん</span>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full max-w-md px-6 mb-8">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end mb-6">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-serif">今週の平均</h2>
    </div>

    <div class="flex justify-between gap-4">
      <% [
        { label: 'こころの負担', val: @stress_percent },
        { label: 'からだの疲れ', val: @fatigue_percent }
      ].each do |item| %>

        <%
          graph_color = if item[:val] >= 80
                          "#ef4444" # 赤
                        elsif item[:val] >= 60
                          "#eab308" # 黄
                        else
                          "#5a6358" # 緑
                        end
        %>

        <div class="flex-1 flex flex-col items-center">
          <div class="w-28 h-28 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-2 relative"
               style="background: conic-gradient(<%= graph_color %> <%= item[:val] %>%, #f1f0ee 0);">
            
            <%# 内側の白い円 %>
            <div class="w-[calc(100%-8px)] h-[calc(100%-8px)] bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center">
              <div class="text-center">
                <span class="text-xl font-bold text-stone-700"><%= item[:val] %>%</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <span class="text-[10px] text-stone-400 font-medium"><%= item[:label] %></span>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="w-full max-w-md px-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 mb-8">
    <div class="bg-stone-100/50 rounded-[32px] p-6 border border-stone-100">
      <div class="mb-4 text-stone-600">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M14.828 14.828a4 4 0 01-5.656 0M9 10h.01M15 10h.01M21 12a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">心の波</h4>
      <p class="text-[10px] text-stone-400 leading-tight">穏やかな上昇傾向です</p>
    </div>

    <div class="bg-stone-100/50 rounded-[32px] p-6 border border-stone-100">
      <div class="mb-4 text-stone-600">
        <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
          <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M20.354 15.354A9 9 0 018.646 3.646 9.003 9.003 0 0012 21a9.003 9.003 0 008.354-5.646z" />
        </svg>
      </div>
      <h4 class="font-bold text-sm mb-1">睡眠の質</h4>
      <p class="text-[10px] text-stone-400 leading-tight">深い眠りが減少しています</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <%# 3. 今日のアドバイス %>
  <div class="w-full max-w-md px-6 mb-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-[40px] p-8 shadow-sm border border-stone-100 text-center">
      <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
        <div class="p-2 bg-stone-50 rounded-full text-emerald-800">
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-6 w-6" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor">
            <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.747 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.247 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253" />
          </svg>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="text-lg font-serif mb-4">今日のアドバイス</h3>
      <p class="text-stone-500 italic text-sm leading-relaxed px-2">
        「季節の変わり目、少し寝不足が続いているようです。今夜はスマホを置いて、温かいハーブティーと共に、静かな読書時間を15分だけ設めてみませんか。」
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="pb-10">
    <%= link_to "体調を記録する", new_health_record_path, 
        class: "px-10 py-4 bg-[#d17770] text-white rounded-2xl hover:bg-[#cc6a63] shadow-lg transition-all inline-block font-medium" %>
  </div>
</div>